{"body": "If that's correct then the entire actionpack/test/controller/filters_test.rb file is not necessary. Most, if not all of the tests there, are testing the filters (ActiveSupport::Callback) on controllers.\r\nI think they are necessary, because we are making sure that the filters both work on controllers and models, thus future proofing the filters in the controllers in case the implementation changes... \r\nIf that's not necessary, then we should clean up that test file... it's indeed testing the same code, implemented by ActiveSupport::Callback", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/20524900", "created_at": "2013-07-05T15:33:50Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11294#issuecomment-20524900", "updated_at": "2013-07-05T15:33:50Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 11294, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iwiznia/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iwiznia/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iwiznia/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/iwiznia", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iwiznia/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/iwiznia", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iwiznia/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/f81560e8e8743d0df6a467b88df31bbc?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fe0eabf980955325a87a94106b85d1664.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iwiznia/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iwiznia/received_events", "gravatar_id": "f81560e8e8743d0df6a467b88df31bbc", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iwiznia/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "iwiznia", "type": "User", "id": 521248, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iwiznia/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237d68abd3543c1510082d9"}, "id": 20524900, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/11294"}
